cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IT, cs.NE, cs.GR 

The paper deals with image restoration using an artificial neural network, which is a common technique in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of holographic memory and quick response codes suggests that the paper may also fall under multimedia (cs.MM) and information theory (cs.IT). The paper also involves the use of machine learning (cs.NE) and graphics (cs.GR) techniques.
